Learning Activities & Resources: Watched videos on youtube on how to create a Joomla website on local host (XAMMP). I was struggling to setup XAMMP local server on my pc in the begining. Tried watching youtube solutions but I could not fix the "phpmyadmin error".
It kept saying mysqli missing even though I enabled that extension. So, I decided to to go to a hosting service online(Host Gator). After watching a few more tutorials on how to install joomla and how to navigate and make changes into the backend I learned that
the user interface og Joomla is quite confusing at times and I kept getting lost. After watchinga few more videos and spending eons I am getting the hang of it but need to explore/design more in the following week. Useful links: 
